N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4022.15 - Action by the commission

State Regulations

Whenever under this Subchapter a matter has been
referred to the commission, the commission shall take such action as the
commission shall deem proper and appropriate under the law. Notes
